<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    /* CSS styles for the menu header */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-image: url('/images/bg.png');
      background-size: cover;
    }
    .menu {
      background-color: #FF4500;
      padding: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .menu ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
    }
    .menu li {
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .menu a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .menu .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }
    .menu .logo span {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .menu .logo img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      margin-right: 5px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .menu .about-button {
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .menu .about-button a {
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .menu .icons {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .menu .icons a {
      margin-left: 10px;
    }
    .menu .icons img {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(39%) sepia(99%) saturate(3167%) hue-rotate(342deg) brightness(108%) contrast(100%);
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .popup-container {
      position: fixed;
      top: 2%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 800px; /* Limit the width of the popup container */
      height: 90vh; /* Limit the height of the popup container */
      overflow-y: auto; /* Enable vertical scrolling */
      background-color: #ffD; /* Set the background color to white */
      color: #000; /* Text color set to black */
      border: 2px solid #FF4500;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      z-index: 9999;
    }
    .popup .menu-bar {
      background-color: #111;
      padding: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .popup .menu-bar span {
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: auto;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .popup .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .popup .header img {
      width: 33%; /* Set the headshot width to 33% of the popup width */
      max-width: 200px; /* Limit the headshot size */
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .popup .resume-section {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    .popup .resume-section h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .popup .resume-section p {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="menu">
    <div class="logo">
      <span>Peppers Galore!</span>
    </div>
    <div class="logo">
      <a href="/">
        <img src="/images/pepper-logo.png" alt="Pepper Logo">
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="icons">
      <div class="about-button">
        <a onclick="openPopup()">About</a>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:willpybus4@gmail.com">
        <img src="/images/email-icon.png" alt="Email Icon">
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/will-pybus/" target="_blank">
        <img src="/images/linkedin-icon.png" alt="LinkedIn Icon">
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="popup" class="popup" style="display: none;">
    <div class="menu-bar">
      <span onclick="closePopup()">&lt;BACK</span>
    </div>
     <div class="header">
    <img src="/images/headshot.jpg" alt="Headshot" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;">
    <h2>William Pybus</h2>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> Houston, Texas, United States</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> willpybus4@gmail.com</p>
  </div>

    <div class="summary">
      <h3>Summary</h3>
      <p>I have been coding C++ since I was 12 years old. I am making a transition from coding and IT into the cybersecurity field and am learning Rust in advance to keep up with the current trend. I am familiar with technical support and have previously set up and programmed workstations for engineers. My first computer was Linux, then I moved to a MacBook, and now I use Windows most often, but I still keep up to date on manipulating Linux systems.</p>
    </div>

