      <p><strong>CSAT Solutions LP</strong></p>
      <p>Jan 2020 - Apr 2020 (4 months)</p>
      <p>Performed troubleshooting and repair of model a1286 MacBooks.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="education">
      <h3>Education</h3>
      <p><strong>The University of Texas at Austin</strong></p>
      <p>Cybersecurity Certification Course</p>
      <p>Mar 2023 - Sep 2023</p>
    </div>

    <div class="skills">
      <h3>Skills</h3>
      <p>Node.js • Ethical Hacking • Penetration Testing • VMware • Cybersecurity • Chemistry • Microsoft Excel • Troubleshooting • Computer Repair • Power Tools</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function openPopup() {
      document.getElementById("popup").style.display = "block";
    }

    function closePopup() {
      document.getElementById("popup").style.display = "none";
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
